title: Naruto Shippuden English Subbed Complete 1-356
description:
First time uploading so excuse me if something goes astray.

This is the complete Naruto Shippuden collection of episodes up to 357.  Some of the episodes I had to record online because I couldn't find them available anywhere to torrent them, mainly episodes pre 150.

All other episodes I have compiled from others to form a single collection.  I will seed for a while to get this going.  Please do your part and seed as well.
